IDEX to the moon is a fascinating phrase if you think about it What is your definition of to the moon I bet mine is different than yours And yours is different than most others To the moon might mean to 5 for some and 20 for others Maybe even 100 for some It simply depends on where you bought in at and what your goals are I really like this stock and do believe its going to my moonits just going to be a long journey For me this wont make me rich in a week month or year It will be at least a few years but the long hold will be worth it in my opinion Stay patient A few years from now will be here before you know it
